Lyrics
----------------------------------------
BATTLE ON THE EDGE

Leave others in the dust
Don't let them get in your way
Fight the monsters, Show your power
Massive steel, You wild thing

Fumes of burning hot blood of the car
Storming around me

Engine's hot, but I stay cool
Tighten you seat Belt
Engine's plays a rockin beat
Show me what you can do

Engine's hot, but I stay cool
Kick the gas to the floor
Engine's plays a rockin beat
Show me what you can do

Victory is yours

-Words by Ryoichi Hasegawa & Fumio Ito (SEGA)
-Music Composed by Fumio Ito (SEGA)

-Vocal Performance & Arrangement : Dennis St. James
-Drums : Rod Morganstain
-Bass : Zev Katz
-E.Guitar : Reb Beach
-Other Synth Programming : Fumio Ito


