I CAN DO IT

For split second, I give everything I got
I know, I can do it

My sight goes fading black, My sense flashes razor sharp
I'd give my life for this excitement
Body creaks, and tires scream, I'll take every chance
Thats what I'm here for, Cheer of the crowds
Thats what, I deserve

I'll grab on to your dreams, By any means I got
I know, I can do it

My sight goes fading black, My sense flashes razor sharp
I'd give my life for this excitement
Iron beast, roaring in front of me
Shaking the crowd, Going wild
Shaking the track, Even the earth

My sight goes fading black, My sense flashes razor sharp
I'd give my life for this excitement

My sight goes fading black, My sense flashes razor sharp
I race to feel this forbidden Ecstasy

My sight goes fading black, My sense flashes razor sharp
I'd give my life for this excitement
Body creaks, and tires scream, I'll take every chance
Thats what I'm here for, Taste of victory
Thats what, I race for

